Developer Terms of Use
des:
Did you know you can travel the world without ever leaving your living room?

Just say "Alexa, open City Travel" and hear what they cities around the world sound like, learn more about the population and new cultures. 

At the moment, City Travel has following cities on the map:

Amsterdam
Bangkok
Barcelona
Beijing
Bergen
Berlin
Brussels
Budapest
Cairo
Paris
Rome
